<A>__{all eyes turn on her again, hearing the reservation in her voice.}
<C>__{margaret }
<D>__{prime minister, with the miners' leader calling today for the army to mutiny in support of the strikes, this seems the wrong time for conciliation.}
<B>__{suddenly all the lights go out.}
<A>__{a lot of `bloody hell' `oh for god's sake'.}
<C>__{heath}
<D>__{be patient. they'll come back on in a minute.}
